600
00:48:56,050 --> 00:48:57,476
Dočerta.

601
00:49:06,769 --> 00:49:07,977
Nevšímajte si nás.

602
00:49:07,978 --> 00:49:10,572
- Len si to vypite.
- To je v poriadku.

603
00:49:19,365 --> 00:49:21,657
